The paper deals with image recognition and retrieval, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of graph databases for storing and querying scene graphs suggests a focus on database systems (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The development of a method for fast approximate retrieval of images suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG).
